title: What's The Big Deal?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Israel Gutierrez debate what they read into Joe Lacob’s comments to Tim Kawakami and if it was a bigger deal that Paolo Banchero looked pretty good last night or Jabari Smith Jr. looked like a role player.
